title: Did not receive my pool party icon?

embed.description: Check your Summoner statistics, MMR, realtime spectate and using powerful global LoL Charts!

body:
You can clearly see on my stats that I played premade 5v5 during the week 15th-21st June however I did not receive any icon.

Anyone else got this problem?

replies.body: Maybe your leaver buster had found something? same thing happened to me
